      "updated": 1775926721899,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1)  Reverser the expression\n2) then change ( -> ) and ) -> ( \n3) perfmr postfix conversion\n4) Reverse the final result ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1)  Reverser the expression\n2) then change ( -> ) and ) -> ( \n3) perfmr postfix conversion\n4) Reverse the final result ",
